Invocation Name: chinese economy facts
des: China’s model of economic development has brought huge success to the country in the last few decades. Alongside its achievements, however, are various implications to uneven growth. For example, China’s nutrition transition displays changing diets that lean more toward unhealthy, less diversified diets. The economic inequalities and rural-urban disparities are also alarming, and environmental pollution together with food safety are raising concerns among Chinese consumers. So everyone must know some facts about Chinese economy.
